.SH NAME
sunshine-navigate - Set navigation destination


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBsunshine navigate   [title] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Set a navigation destination by providing lat/lng coordinates and an optional title.
Use 'navigate show' to view or 'navigate clear' to remove the current destination.


